One person has been arrested in connection with the murder of Hillary Gardee. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - One person has been arrested in connection with the murder of Hillary Gardee. The suspect, in his 30s, will appear in court on Monday. WATCH: Candlelight vigil for Hillary Gardee Gardee was found dead on Tuesday near Mbombela after she went missing on the 29th of April. Mpumalanga police commissioner, Semakaleng Manamela, said police are confident they’ve arrested the right person. READ: Crime in SA | Deadline to find Hillary Gardee killers nears Meanwhile, Gardee's family has commended the arrest of the suspect. Sinawo Tambo, the family spokesperson, says they're battling to come to terms with her death.